com.vectorprint.configuration

Interface EnhancedMap

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Map<String,String[]>, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HiddenBy
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPropertiesDecorator, CachingProperties, FindableProperties, HelpSupportedProperties, ObservableProperties, ParsingProperties, PreparingProperties, ReadonlyProperties, Settings, ThreadSafeProperties

    public interface EnhancedMap
extends Map<String,String[]>, Cloneable, Serializable
    This interface is a suggested way to store values for settings as arrays of String and retrieve settings in the type needed by applications. Values are arrays because support for multiple values will not require splitting intelligence.
    Author:
    Eduard Drenth at VectorPrint.nl
    See Also:
    Settings, AbstractPropertiesDecorator, EnhancedMapBindingFactory
